TUTORIAL

In this series of ZBrush and Rhino tutorials, we'll
learn to reverse engineer a 3D scanned mesh and convert it
to a sculpt-able mesh. You'll learn to import the data into
Rhino, convert it to a NURB model and prepare it for rapid
prototyping. By the end of this ZBrush and Rhino tutorial,
you'll be able to use these industry techniques in Rhino and
ZBrush as part of your modeling pipeline
